               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa ʾIsāyǝyyās “Book of Isaiah” [Is.] (fols. 2ra-56vb)&#xD;
II) Maṣḥafa  mǝssāle “Book of Proverbs” [Prov.] (fols. 57ra-101rb)&#xD;
II-1) Mǝssalǝyatä Sälomon “Proverbs of Solomon” (fols. 57ra-77vb)&#xD;
II-2) Tägśaṣä Sälomon “Admonition of Solomon” (fols. 77vb-82vab)&#xD;
III) Ṭǝbäbä Sälomon “Wisdom of Solomon” [Wis.] (fols. 82va-101rb)&#xD;
IV) Qāla Makbǝb “Word of Ecclesiastes” [Ecc.] (fols. 101rb-111ra)&#xD;
V) Maṣḥafa ʾIyob, Book of Job [Job] (fols. 112ra-141ra)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
