                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I is divided into parts (kǝfǝl) which are followed by a number. The numeration is not reliable and stops after <locus target="34ra">34ra</locus>. Up to <locus target="56ra">56ra</locus>, the scribe left blank spaces for rubricated numerals.</note>
                     <note>Texts II-IV are divided into parts (kǝfǝl), but only at the beginning of Text II-1 they are followed by a number.</note>
                     <note>Text V is divided into parts (kǝfǝl) and chapters (mǝʿrāf) which are followed by numbers up to <locus target="120rb">120rb</locus>.</note>
                  </msItem>
