- Commentaries in Gǝʿǝz and glosses written in the margins, in a secondary hand: <locus target="5r">5r</locus>, 7ra, 7vb, 8ra, 20ra, 37ra, 47va. &#xD;
- Erasures: <locus target="15v">15v</locus>, 38rb, 38va, 50ra, 53vb, 87ra. &#xD;
